# 推荐信 (Letter of Recommendation)
**被推荐人**: 李华 (本科生)
**申请项目**: CMU CS Master

To whom it may concern,

It is my great pleasure to recommend Li Hua. He took my "Advanced Algorithms" course last year and ranked top 5% in the class.

What impressed me most was his final project on "Graph Neural Networks for Traffic Prediction". He not only implemented the baseline but also proposed a novel attention mechanism that improved accuracy by 3%.

Li Hua is not just smart; he is persistent. When he encountered a bug in the CUDA kernel, he spent 3 days debugging it instead of switching to a simpler library.

I strongly support his application.

Sincerely,
Prof. Chen
